The website in question is using our company product images and text, and also claims that they are a national distributor of the product which is untrue and tarnishing our brand.

The Australian trademark number that is being infringed upon is 1392513 relating to the PINK DIET ENERGY DRINK owned by Pink Energy Beverages Pty Ltd.

We advise that any unauthorised advertising, marketing, sale or offering of goods and services by reference to the PINK DIET ENERGY DRINK may be considered as "passing off" our business, name and reputation.
